author: bibryam
msg: Renamed AgreementWorkEffortAppl entity to AgreementWorkEffortApplic in order to change relation types so that assigning WorkEfforts to Agreements is possible w/o specifying an agreementItemSeqId.
Added a migrateAgreementWorkEffortAppl service to migrate existing data to the new entity.
